# Web / JS / TS

- Tooling: bun (runtime/pkg), biome (lint/format), tsc (types).
- Commands:
  - `bun install`
  - `bun run <script>`
  - `bunx biome check .`
  - `bunx biome format --write .`
  - `bunx tsc --noEmit`
- Prefer `bun.lock` (text). `bun.lockb` is accepted if present.
